agentLoopbackIpv6PrefixPrefix.name: agentLoopbackIpv6PrefixPrefix
agentLoopbackIpv6PrefixPrefix.description: The prefix associated with the loopback interface. The data type is used to model the Ipv6 address. It is a binary string of 16 octects in network byte-order. It specifies the IP address of loopback which will be in Ipv6 Format, generated using internal interface number.
